The paper focuses on automatic software development, specifically on code comment generation. This falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also uses a seq2seq neural network, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL). The authors also mention using an open source search engine to retrieve similar code, which suggests the use of information retrieval techniques (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach that outperforms existing methods, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
